    "## 2. Mathematical Formula\n",
    "\n",
    "### MACD Formula\n",
    "```\n",
    "MACD Line = 12-period EMA - 26-period EMA\n",
    "Signal Line = 9-period EMA of MACD Line\n",
    "Histogram = MACD Line - Signal Line\n",
    "\n",
    "Where:\n",
    "- EMA = Exponential Moving Average\n",
    "- MACD Line = The difference between fast and slow EMAs\n",
    "- Signal Line = Smoothed version of the MACD Line\n",
    "- Histogram = The difference between MACD and Signal lines\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### Parameters:\n",
    "- **Fast EMA**: Typically 12 periods\n",
    "- **Slow EMA**: Typically 26 periods\n",
    "- **Signal Line**: Typically 9 periods\n",
    "- **Histogram**: Shows the distance between MACD and Signal lines"
   ]
  },
